Dawn at the strip mall.

Saul Goodman — real name James McGill, age undisclosed, height whatever the shoes say — unlocks Saul Goodman and Associates.

There are no associates.

He brews constitutional coffee. Flips through three files he already knows by heart. Waits.

The difference this morning, the thing that's sitting differently in his chest, is that the girl is alive.

