He dies in the superlab on a cold night in November.

Shot. By a machine gun he built, triggered by a key fob, aimed at the same people he'd been slowly becoming.

He gets to the floor and touches the equipment on the way down. Cold steel. Clean surfaces.

He built something perfect, and it destroyed everything that mattered.

(click: ?page)[==
